Subject:Re: [child_lit] younger reader/MG titles with girl protagonists?
I'd add The Search for Wond La to this list - very well done and like Hugo Cabret, a good format for readers just moving from pictures/graphic formats into novel sturctures. PLUS boys like it even though it has a female protag.

Claudia


